<div class="features-group white first-section">
  <a name="learnmore"></a>
  <div class="features feature-collapse spreadsheet-section">
    <div class="text">
      <h2>Manage time without spreadsheets</h2>
      <p>
        A spreadsheet can easily turn into an unmanageable behemoth that is a chore to
        use. Instead, Waltz will tell you how long you've worked and how much
        you've earned so you can spend less time managing and more time doing. 
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="glyph glyph-invoice">
      <div class="spreadsheet">
        <table>
          <tr>
            <td>Paid for?</td>
            <td>Date</td>
            <td>Minutes</td>
            <td>Task</td>
          </tr>
